<Layout title="About Us - Sacramento Fencing Co." description="Learn about Sacramento Fencing Co's 25+ year history of quality fence installation and repair services in Sacramento County.">
	<section class="hero">
		<div class="container">
			<h1>About Sacramento Fencing Co.</h1>
			<p>Building trust and quality fences throughout Sacramento since 1998</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="our-story">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="story-content">
				<div class="story-text">
					<h2>Our Story</h2>
					<p>Sacramento Fencing Co. was founded in 1998 by Mike Rodriguez, a third-generation Sacramento native with a passion for craftsmanship and a deep commitment to serving his community. What began as a small family business with just a pickup truck and unwavering dedication has grown into Sacramento County's most trusted and respected fencing contractor.</p>
					
					<p>Mike learned the construction trade working alongside his father, who immigrated to Sacramento in the 1970s and spent decades building homes and businesses throughout the Central Valley. The values instilled in Mike from day one—honest work, fair pricing, treating every customer like family, and taking pride in craftsmanship—remain the bedrock of our business today.</p>
					
					<p>Over the past 25+ years, we've had the privilege of installing and repairing thousands of fences throughout Sacramento County. Our growth has been fueled entirely by satisfied customers who refer their friends, family, and neighbors. This organic growth is a testament to the quality of our work and the relationships we build with every client.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="story-image">
					<div class="image-placeholder">
						<div class="placeholder-icon">📸</div>
						<h3>Company Photo</h3>
						<p>Mike Rodriguez & The<br/>Sacramento Fencing Co. Team</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="values">
		<div class="container">
			<h2>Our Core Values</h2>
			<div class="values-grid">
				<div class="value-item">
					<div class="value-icon">🔨</div>
					<h3>Quality Craftsmanship</h3>
					<p>We take immense pride in every fence we install. Using only premium materials and time-tested techniques, we build fences that stand strong against Sacramento's varied weather conditions and look beautiful for decades.</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="value-item">
					<div class="value-icon">🤝</div>
					<h3>Honest Business Practices</h3>
					<p>Fair pricing, transparent communication, and absolutely no surprise charges. We provide detailed written estimates and stick to our word every time. Your trust is infinitely more valuable than any single sale.</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="value-item">
					<div class="value-icon">👨‍👩‍👧‍👦</div>
					<h3>Family Values</h3>
					<p>As a family-owned and operated business, we understand the importance of home and community. We treat your property with the same care and respect we would give our own family's home.</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="value-item">
					<div class="value-icon">🌱</div>
					<h3>Community Commitment</h3>
					<p>Born and raised in Sacramento, we're deeply committed to giving back to our community. We support local suppliers, hire local workers, and actively participate in community events and charitable causes.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="team">
		<div class="container">
			<h2>Meet Our Team</h2>
			<div class="team-grid">
				<div class="team-member">
					<div class="member-photo">
						<div class="photo-placeholder">👨‍💼</div>
					</div>
					<h3>Mike Rodriguez</h3>
					<p class="title">Founder & Owner</p>
					<p>With over 30 years in the construction industry and 25+ years leading Sacramento Fencing Co., Mike personally oversees every project to ensure it meets our exacting standards. When not building fences, he enjoys coaching youth baseball and volunteering at local community events.</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="team-member">
					<div class="member-photo">
						<div class="photo-placeholder">👨‍🔧</div>
					</div>
					<h3>Carlos Martinez</h3>
					<p class="title">Lead Installation Supervisor</p>
					<p>Carlos has been with Sacramento Fencing Co. for 18 years and leads our installation crews with unmatched expertise. His keen attention to detail and creative problem-solving skills have made him invaluable to our team and beloved by our customers.</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="team-member">
					<div class="member-photo">
						<div class="photo-placeholder">👩‍💼</div>
					</div>
					<h3>Maria Rodriguez</h3>
					<p class="title">Operations Manager</p>
					<p>Maria handles all customer service, project scheduling, and coordination with her signature warmth and professionalism. Her bilingual abilities and organizational skills ensure every customer interaction is positive and every project runs smoothly.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="achievements">
		<div class="container">
			<h2>Our Achievements & Milestones</h2>
			<div class="achievements-grid">
				<div class="achievement">
					<div class="achievement-number">25+</div>
					<h3>Years in Business</h3>
					<p>Proudly serving Sacramento since 1998</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="achievement">
					<div class="achievement-number">8,500+</div>
					<h3>Fences Installed</h3>
					<p>Residential and commercial projects completed</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="achievement">
					<div class="achievement-number">99%</div>
					<h3>Customer Satisfaction</h3>
					<p>Based on verified customer reviews</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="achievement">
					<div class="achievement-number">A+</div>
					<h3>BBB Rating</h3>
					<p>Better Business Bureau accredited since 2005</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="certifications">
		<div class="container">
			<h2>Licenses & Certifications</h2>
			<div class="cert-grid">
				<div class="cert-item">
					<div class="cert-icon">🏗️</div>
					<h3>Licensed Contractor</h3>
					<p>California Contractor License #984567<br/>Fully bonded and insured</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="cert-item">
					<div class="cert-icon">🛡️</div>
					<h3>Comprehensive Insurance</h3>
					<p>$2 Million General Liability Coverage<br/>Workers' Compensation Insurance</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="cert-item">
					<div class="cert-icon">⭐</div>
					<h3>BBB Accredited Business</h3>
					<p>A+ Rating with Better Business Bureau<br/>Accredited member since 2005</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="cert-item">
					<div class="cert-icon">🌿</div>
					<h3>Environmental Responsibility</h3>
					<p>Green building practices certified<br/>Sustainable material sourcing</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="community">
		<div class="container">
			<h2>Community Involvement</h2>
			<div class="community-content">
				<p>We believe in giving back to the Sacramento community that has supported our family business for over two decades. Our involvement includes:</p>
				
				<div class="community-grid">
					<div class="community-item">
						<div class="community-icon">🏀</div>
						<h3>Youth Sports Sponsorship</h3>
						<p>We proudly sponsor multiple Little League teams and youth basketball clubs throughout Sacramento, providing uniforms, equipment, and field improvements.</p>
					</div>
					
					<div class="community-item">
						<div class="community-icon">🏠</div>
						<h3>Habitat for Humanity</h3>
						<p>Our crew regularly volunteers time and materials for Habitat for Humanity home builds, helping provide affordable housing for local families.</p>
					</div>
					
					<div class="community-item">
						<div class="community-icon">🎒</div>
						<h3>Educational Partnerships</h3>
						<p>We partner with local high schools and trade programs to provide internships and hands-on construction skills training to students.</p>
					</div>
					
					<div class="community-item">
						<div class="community-icon">🚨</div>
						<h3>First Responder Appreciation</h3>
						<p>We offer special discounts to police officers, firefighters, EMTs, and military personnel as our way of saying thank you for their service.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="testimonials">
		<div class="container">
			<h2>What Our Community Says</h2>
			<div class="testimonials-grid">
				<div class="testimonial">
					<p>"Mike and his team are absolute professionals. They installed a beautiful cedar fence around our entire backyard in just two days. The quality is outstanding and the price was very fair. Highly recommended!"</p>
					<div class="customer">
						<strong>Robert & Susan Chen</strong><br>
						<span>Land Park Residents</span>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="testimonial">
					<p>"After getting quotes from several companies, Sacramento Fencing Co. stood out for their professionalism and attention to detail. They delivered exactly what they promised, on time and on budget."</p>
					<div class="customer">
						<strong>Jennifer Martinez</strong><br>
						<span>Elk Grove Business Owner</span>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="testimonial">
					<p>"We've used Sacramento Fencing Co. for three different properties over the years. Their consistency in quality and service is remarkable. They treat every job like it's their most important one."</p>
					<div class="customer">
						<strong>David Thompson</strong><br>
						<span>Property Manager, Roseville</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="cta">
		<div class="container">
			<h2>Ready to Work with Sacramento's Most Trusted Fencing Company?</h2>
			<p>Join thousands of satisfied customers who have chosen Sacramento Fencing Co. for their residential and commercial fencing needs. Experience the difference that 25+ years of expertise and commitment to quality makes.</p>
			<a href="/contact" class="btn">Get Your Free Estimate Today</a>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

